{"word":"G4790 - συγκοινωνέω - synkoinōnéō - soong-koy-no-neh'-o - Communicate with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγκοινωνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synkoinōnéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soong-koy-no-neh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Communicate with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உடன்படு"},{"paragraph":"to become a partaker together with others"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2841 - κοινωνέω - koinōnéō - koy-no-neh'-o/2841\">G2841</a>; to <i>share</i> in company <i>with</i>, that is, <i>co-participate</i> in: - communicate (have fellowship) with, be partaker of.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2839/2839\">G2839</a>, <a href=\"#/G2840/2840\">G2840</a>, <a href=\"#/G2841/2841\">G2841</a>, <a href=\"#/G2842/2842\">G2842</a>, <a href=\"#/G2843/2843\">G2843</a>, <a href=\"#/G2844/2844\">G2844</a>, <a href=\"#/G4790/4790\">G4790</a>, <a href=\"#/G4791/4791\">G4791</a>"}]}